    metaTitle: "Things to Do in Ajaccio (2026) — Napoleon, Beaches & the Sanguinaires",
    metaDesc:
      "Ajaccio's Napoleon heritage, its old town and market, the golden beaches and the boat trip out to the Sanguinaire islands.",
    category: "city-guide",
    emoji: "🌅",
